<name>GLOBAL INTELLIGENCE PLATFORM — MASTER KML (consolidated)</name>
<description><![CDATA[
<b>Consolidated master overview</b> — every geographic layer from the project in one file.<br/>
Merges the live v13 dashboard theaters (Week 10, 29 Jun 2026) with all originally-uploaded intelligence layers:
chokepoints, oil infrastructure (2021-26), energy/utility grid, oil-sector delta, and the Nigeria non-kinetic stability layer.<br/>
Toggle folders on/off in Google Earth to switch between analytical layers.<br/>
<i>Total: 249 placemarks across 6 layer-groups. Sources: ISW/CTP, ACLED, Crisis Group, Yale HRL, IRC + user OSINT uploads.</i>
]]></description>

